statements: SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_maintenance_schedule;
SELECT id, maintenance_type FROM wind_turbine_maintenance_schedule WHERE completed = TRUE;
SELECT turbine_id, maintenance_date FROM wind_turbine_maintenance_schedule ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT maintenance_type, maintenance_cost FROM wind_turbine_maintenance_schedule WHERE maintenance_cost > 5000;
SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_maintenance_schedule WHERE maintenance_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';
SELECT id, maintenance_type, maintenance_cost FROM wind_turbine_maintenance_schedule WHERE maintenance_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30' ORDER BY maintenance_cost DESC;
SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_maintenance_schedule WHERE turbine_id = 3 AND completed = true ORDER BY maintenance_date ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT maintenance_type FROM wind_turbine_maintenance_schedule;
SELECT id, turbine_id, maintenance_type, maintenance_date, maintenance_cost, completed FROM wind_turbine_maintenance_schedule WHERE maintenance_type LIKE 'Annual%' ORDER BY maintenance_date;
SELECT AVG(maintenance_cost) AS avg_cost, MAX(maintenance_cost) AS max_cost, MIN(maintenance_cost) AS min_cost FROM wind_turbine_maintenance_schedule;
SELECT turbine_id, location, energy_production FROM WindTurbine;
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine ORDER BY location ASC;
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine WHERE energy_production > 1000;
SELECT turbine_id, last_maintenance_date FROM WindTurbine WHERE last_maintenance_date < '2022-01-01';
SELECT turbine_id, scheduled_date, description FROM MaintenanceSchedule ORDER BY scheduled_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine WHERE energy_production > 1000 ORDER BY location ASC
SELECT location, energy_production FROM WindTurbine WHERE last_maintenance_date < '2021-08-01' AND maintenance_interval > INTERVAL '3 months'

SELECT turbine_id, location, last_maintenance_date FROM WindTurbine JOIN MaintenanceSchedule ON WindTurbine.turbine_id = MaintenanceSchedule.turbine_id WHERE scheduled_date < '2021-12-31' ORDER BY scheduled_date DESC
SELECT * FROM MaintenanceSchedule WHERE description ILIKE '%inspection%' OR description ILIKE '%repair%'

SELECT location, energy_production, EXTRACT(MONTH FROM last_maintenance_date) AS maintenance_month FROM WindTurbine WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM last_maintenance_date) = 2021 ORDER BY maintenance_month ASC
SELECT * FROM WindTurbineMaintenanceSchedule;
SELECT turbine_id, maintenance_date FROM WindTurbineMaintenanceSchedule ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT model, commission_date FROM Turbines WHERE manufacturer='ABC Corp';
SELECT technician_id, COUNT(*) FROM WindTurbineMaintenanceSchedule GROUP BY technician_id;
SELECT id, specialization FROM Technicians WHERE hire_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM WindTurbineMaintenanceSchedule WHERE maintenance_type = 'Scheduled Maintenance';
SELECT turbine_id, maintenance_date FROM WindTurbineMaintenanceSchedule WHERE technician_id = 123 ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT t.model, t.manufacturer, tm.specialization FROM Turbines t JOIN Technicians tm ON t.id = tm.id WHERE t.commission_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT DISTINCT t.location_id, ts.name FROM Turbines t, Technicians ts WHERE t.location_id = 456 AND ts.specialization = 'Electrical';
SELECT t.id, ts.name, tm.hire_date FROM Turbines t JOIN Technicians ts ON t.location_id = ts.id JOIN Technicians tm ON t.model = tm.specialization;

SELECT location, manufacturer FROM WindTurbines ORDER BY location ASC
SELECT * FROM WindTurbines WHERE manufacturer='ABC Inc.'
SELECT id, installation_date FROM WindTurbines WHERE location='Texas' ORDER BY installation_date DESC
SELECT schedule_id, maintenance_type FROM MaintenanceSchedule
SELECT * FROM WindTurbines;
SELECT manufacturer, installation_date FROM WindTurbines ORDER BY installation_date DESC;
SELECT location, manufacturer, installation_date FROM WindTurbines WHERE location='New York';
SELECT * FROM MaintenanceSchedule JOIN WindTurbines ON MaintenanceSchedule.turbine_id = WindTurbines.id;

SELECT WindTurbines.location, MaintenanceSchedule.schedule_date, MaintenanceLogs.technician FROM WindTurbines JOIN MaintenanceSchedule ON WindTurbines.id = MaintenanceSchedule.turbine_id JOIN MaintenanceLogs ON MaintenanceSchedule.schedule_id = MaintenanceLogs.schedule_id ORDER BY MaintenanceSchedule.schedule_date ASC;

SELECT id, location FROM WindTurbine ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT model FROM WindTurbine WHERE last_maintenance_date < '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM MaintenanceSchedule WHERE maintenance_type = 'routine' ORDER BY scheduled_date ASC;
